Detailed Description

The particles aspect of the code. At present this evolves either fluid or inertial particles in the code. The type of particle is set by the particle_type parameter in run.in, if a particle is quasi then the superfluid velocity if used to evolve the particle using the stiff_solver and hamiltonian module. Fluid particles use the normal fluid velocity in the future we should split quasi and fluid particles into separate arrays and modules.
